title: Eddie Has To Explain Something Embarrassing To His In-Laws + Dr. Oz On If Diet Soda Is Better For You + Jon Bon Jovi On Not Performing An Encore
itunes:title: Eddie Has To Explain Something Embarrassing To His In-Laws + Dr. Oz On If Diet Soda Is Better For You + Jon Bon Jovi On Not Performing An Encore
description:
Bobby laughed at Eddie's embarrassing situation with his in-laws. We ask Dr. Oz all our big health questions. Jon Bon Jovi comes on the show for the first time to talk about his new collaboration with Jennifer Nettles. Plus, Bobby asks him if he ever skips an encore at his concerts.
